Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.94,0:00:34.01,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Twenty more minutes...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.86,0:00:49.45,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked dark, cramped spaces,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.45,0:00:51.82,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd bury my face deep in my hood
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.82,0:00:54.20,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,My eyes resented the heartless world,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:57.95,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,but yearned for love
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.87,0:01:04.59,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I liked being soaked by the rain,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.59,0:01:06.96,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,because my face looked better clouded over
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.96,0:01:09.60,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I pretended to be afraid of the storm
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.60,0:01:12.43,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,while waiting for the sky to burst
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.54,0:01:19.39,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum through the light's distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.39,0:01:23.81,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make thunder roar
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.81,0:01:29.61,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum beyond the pain
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.61,0:01:33.74,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? This fierce \Npounding is out of control
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.74,0:01:39.80,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Strum in a harmonizing quartet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.80,0:01:43.79,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to cause a revolution
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.79,0:01:49.80,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,Drum in a lamenting forte
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.80,0:01:54.55,Songs_OP,OP,0000,0000,0000,,What can I do? My savage \Nnature is beyond wild
