Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.22,0:02:16.60,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have a talk about our future as a band!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.60,0:02:18.32,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Meetup at Starry tomorrow, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.65,0:02:21.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The joy of getting LOINE messages\Nfrom someone who wasn't a relative
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.71,0:02:23.66,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,got me this far, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.53,0:02:26.69,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I walk in there looking \Nlike the hick I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.69,0:02:30.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,they'll all look at me \Nlike I don't belong there...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.17,0:02:34.17,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I made it in last time because \NI was with Nijika-chan, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.06,0:02:38.05,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if anyone's there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.07,0:02:43.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I wish I had someone to go in with.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.72,0:02:45.74,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Five minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.36,0:02:48.89,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll wait five minutes, then go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.47,0:02:51.57,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, ten...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.57,0:02:52.59,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.59,0:02:54.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll totally go in after fifteen.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.92,0:02:58.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What's she doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.68,0:02:59.13,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bo—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.13,0:02:59.99,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.48,0:03:02.03,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna watch a little longer.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.03,0:03:04.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Could you please stop enjoying this?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.15,0:03:06.70,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.70,0:03:11.57,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby declare the first Kessoku Band \Nmembers' meeting... open!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.57,0:03:12.40,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Round of applause!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.40,0:03:14.98,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Clappy clappy clap clap clap!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.98,0:03:16.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.94,0:03:21.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait. We barely know each other, \Nso I dunno what to talk about!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.83,0:03:23.47,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She just admitted it!
Dialogue: 1,0:03:23.79,0:03:26.65,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I brought this for just such an occasion.
