Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.16,0:03:49.00,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Wait, don't you both \Ngo to the same school...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.08,0:03:52.96,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs18\c&H110B07&\pos(332.5,287.5)}Talk about School
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.00,0:03:50.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, Shima High!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.80,0:03:52.96,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We chose it 'cause it's close to home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.96,0:03:55.59,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, so you live in Shimo-Kitazawa...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.59,0:03:58.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Bocchi-chan, don't you go to Shuka High?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.25,0:04:00.21,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Shouldn't you live around here too?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.21,0:04:03.91,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, I live out-of-prefecture. \NTwo-hour commute each way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.91,0:04:04.68,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Two hours?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.68,0:04:05.43,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.84,0:04:09.84,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted a high school \Nwhere nobody knew my past.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.84,0:04:11.60,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, enough TAS!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.60,0:04:13.49,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.49,0:04:16.55,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I spend most of my time at school alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.55,0:04:20.52,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,so I don't have any f-fun \Nstories to contribute...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.52,0:04:21.61,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, it's okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.61,0:04:24.15,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo doesn't have many friends either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.15,0:04:26.17,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, just Nijika.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.17,0:04:27.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Tha-thump.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.31,0:04:32.18,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san is just like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.54,0:04:35.79,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(521,1)\fnGeorgia\b0\c&H525A56&\3c&HEAF2EE&\bord1.8\4c&H5CC7D5&\shad2\pos(497,256.5)}Loneliness Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.68,0:04:35.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,On days off, she does urban exploration
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.79,0:04:37.96,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and visits second-hand clothing shops...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.96,0:04:39.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, she's not...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.72,0:04:42.55,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo-san {\i0}likes{\i1} being alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.72,0:04:47.43,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Someone with social anxiety could never \Nenter a clothing shop on her own!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.43,0:04:49.89,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\c&H3420BE&\bord1\3c&H39367A&\frz15.09\pos(485,75)\t(23,2442,\fscx50\fscy50)}Lonely
