Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.47,0:04:58.03,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I nearly fell into the trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.03,0:05:00.07,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, let's enjoy the conversation!
