Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.24,0:05:09.66,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,T-TAFM...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:14.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I like Japanese punk, like mellow core.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.20,0:05:16.54,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I like techno kayo,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.54,0:05:19.71,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,and lately I've been checking \Nthe Saudi Arabian charts—
