Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.48,0:05:38.96,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,are glitter-coated upbeat songs \Nthat include words like
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.96,0:05:44.02,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,"summer," "blue sea," \N"fireworks," "puppy love,"
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.02,0:05:47.86,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,and other things irrelevant to \Nher personal school experience!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.99,0:05:51.97,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Such words plunge me into a deep melancholy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.80,0:05:51.30,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.97,0:05:52.68,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,By the same token,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.68,0:05:56.95,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,you love bands that write about the \Nbleakness of their high school years, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.53,0:05:56.95,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.95,0:05:58.32,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.32,0:06:03.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But sometimes I find out a band I love\Nwas super popular in school,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.36,0:06:07.47,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and they suddenly feel \Nlike strangers to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.13,0:06:10.45,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, please! Come back to our planet, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.45,0:06:13.83,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Rock resonates as the music \Nof the perpetual underdog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.83,0:06:16.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Is it really rock if it's \Nsung by life's winners?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.08,0:06:18.18,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm trying to establish some ties, here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.18,0:06:19.76,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Since we're named after zip ties.
