Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.64,0:06:21.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.22,0:06:24.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Our first concert was instrumentals only,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.24,0:06:26.20,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but I'd like to have vocals next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.20,0:06:27.90,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.90,0:06:31.41,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The guitarist who ran off was \Ngonna be our singer, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:33.88,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Where'd she even go, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.32,0:06:37.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The runaway guitarist...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.48,0:06:41.34,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she's socially anxious like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:43.86,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No, there's no way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.86,0:06:46.92,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If you're really socially anxious, \Nyou {\i0}can't{\i1} even run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.92,0:06:49.86,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We've gotta find a new vocalist.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.86,0:06:52.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I can't sing for squat, myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.08,0:06:53.47,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, can you—
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.28,0:06:56.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... Figured.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.72,0:06:59.06,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Wh-What about Ryo-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:01.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(232,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&HC2C1B1&\3c&HBF7051&\bord2\pos(175,66.5)\frz22.62}Sob
