Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.73,0:07:02.26,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,If I were to serve as frontman,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(191,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&HC2C1B1&\3c&HBF7051&\bord2\frz15.18\pos(150,208.5)}Sob
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.73,0:07:02.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(191,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&HC2C1B1&\3c&HBF7051&\bord2\frz22.6\pos(467,142.5)}Sob
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.26,0:07:05.30,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,I'd overwhelm the band and crush it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.73,0:07:03.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(192,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&HC2C1B1&\3c&HBF7051&\bord2\pos(175,66.5)\frz22.62}Sob
