Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.30,0:07:07.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Where do you get that \Nwellspring of confidence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.73,0:07:06.69,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(191,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&HC2C1B1&\3c&HBF7051&\bord2\frz15.18\pos(150,208.5)}Sob
