Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.73,0:07:07.44,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(196,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&HC2C1B1&\3c&HBF7051&\bord2\pos(471.5,145)\frz346.6}Sob
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.73,0:07:09.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.04,0:07:11.13,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'd like a little of that \Nconfidence for myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.13,0:07:12.21,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:14.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's find a vocalist and write a song!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.72,0:07:16.15,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Ryo can write the music,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.15,0:07:19.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and if you've got off-limits words, \NBocchi-chan, you should write the lyrics!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.50,0:07:21.33,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.33,0:07:23.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well? Great idea, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:27.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The nine years of lunch breaks \NI spent in school libraries...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.24,0:07:29.30,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Was it all in preparation for this moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.30,0:07:30.86,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,So, what will you do, Nijika?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.17,0:07:33.86,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.63,0:07:38.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Next, talk about quotas!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.10,0:07:39.60,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Just shamelessly dodged that one, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.02,0:07:43.09,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um... What are quotas?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.09,0:07:46.15,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The concert we did yesterday \Nis called a "booked concert."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.43,0:07:49.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's where the club assigns \Nthe band a ticket quota
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.44,0:07:51.65,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,to make sure enough people come.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.65,0:07:52.85,Default,Club-kun,0000,0000,0000,,Your quota is ten tickets!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.31,0:08:03.62,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anything sold over the quota gets \Nsplit between the club and the band...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.40,0:08:10.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But if they can't bring in \Nenough to meet the quota,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.56,0:08:13.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,the band has to pay the rest out of pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:16.18,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,So until you get popular, it's a money pit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.18,0:08:17.72,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's very concise!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.72,0:08:21.49,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,A bunch of my friends came \Nto yesterday's concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.49,0:08:23.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,so we managed to meet our quota, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.58,0:08:25.91,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,After that performance, \Nthey likely won't be back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.91,0:08:27.73,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You said it!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.73,0:08:31.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And Ryo's got no friends, \Nso she'll be no help...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.11,0:08:32.85,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, do you—
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.30,0:08:35.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, sorry! Forget what I said.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.36,0:08:37.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Just please lose the dead fish stare!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.72,0:08:40.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've got plenty of imaginary friends, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.84,0:08:42.48,Default,Guitar Man,0000,0000,0000,,You rock, Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.48,0:08:44.37,Default,Mai-kun,0000,0000,0000,,Living national treasure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.37,0:08:48.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, since we'll need tens of thousands \Nof yen before our next concert,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.60,0:08:52.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,let's get jobs to cover \Nthe quota and equipment!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.72,0:08:54.38,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.91,0:08:55.88,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Jobs?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.31,0:08:57.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's the loudest I've ever heard you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.05,0:08:59.70,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.70,0:09:01.28,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to work. Too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.28,0:09:02.77,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Society is too scary!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.34,0:09:07.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,A piggy bank?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.04,0:09:12.90,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,M-My mom was saving up for my wedding...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.90,0:09:14.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But you can have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.40,0:09:16.10,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Just... Please, no job...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.10,0:09:18.67,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make us the bad guys here!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.52,0:09:19.39,DefaultTop,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, we'll take good care of—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.67,0:09:19.96,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're {\i1}not{\i0} taking it!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.96,0:09:22.54,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We can't take money that \Nmeans that much to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.51,0:09:25.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.20,0:09:26.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I don't wanna work!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.72,0:09:28.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Because...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.86,0:09:33.55,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welcome... Sh-Should I warm... up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.73,0:09:33.55,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It'd totally be like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:38.93,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\c&H8F938D&\fs12\3c&HFBFEFB&\bord3.5\pos(132,55)}Not this cashier who can't even make eye contact lmaoooooooooooooo
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.36,0:09:38.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Welcome... Sh-Should I warm... up?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.62,0:09:38.93,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And then that...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.93,0:09:43.77,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\an4\fs16\3c&H000401&\bord2\i1\4c&HDA76F3&\shad2\pos(134,296.5)}Breaking\N{\i0\fs20\shad0}Defendant Hitori Gotoh's First Trial
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.19,DefaultTop,Prosecutor,0000,0000,0000,,For the crime of creeping out the customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.19,0:09:43.77,DefaultTop,Prosecutor,0000,0000,0000,,we seek the death penalty!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.00,0:09:46.28,Default,Judge,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, here comes the ruling...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.28,0:09:47.29,Default,Judge,0000,0000,0000,,Death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.69,0:09:50.19,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And then that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.72,0:09:51.53,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,...cchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.53,0:09:52.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.77,0:09:53.96,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.24,0:09:58.04,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You weren't listening, were you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.04,0:09:59.30,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.30,0:10:01.07,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What were you saying?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.80,0:10:04.03,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,You should work here with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.03,0:10:05.11,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.88,0:10:07.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:09.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You won't have to be scared \Nif you're with me and Ryo!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.08,0:10:12.75,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnComic Sans MS\fs18\c&H110B07&\pos(332.5,287.5)}Talk about Quotas
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.84,0:10:12.75,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,It's a homey and harmonious place to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.70,0:10:17.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We can serve drinks, and clean, \Nand see all kinds of bands!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.32,0:10:17.76,DefaultItalicsTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Don't wanna work... Don't wanna work...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.76,0:10:19.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Well? What do you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.63,0:10:24.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Say no, girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.35,0:10:25.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Say no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.32,0:10:27.98,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You have to say no!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.09,0:10:30.27,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll dwu mwy bwest...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.81,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Really? Thanks so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:33.31,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, girl...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.07,0:10:35.17,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The job'll be more fun if we're all together!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.31,0:10:36.07,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It wouldn't be social anxiety \Nif we had the courage to say no.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.68,0:10:39.63,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll manage the band's funds, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.15,0:10:43.40,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Um... Wouldn't it be better \Nto have Ryo-san do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.40,0:10:44.58,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What's that supposed to mean?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.27,0:10:47.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.00,0:10:50.14,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Believe it or not, \NRyo's a very irresponsible spender.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.04,0:10:54.10,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Her family's rich and she \Ngets a huge allowance,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.71,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but she blows it all on instruments, \Nso she's constantly broke!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.88,0:10:58.65,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.65,0:11:00.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What part of that did you \Ntake as a compliment?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.66,0:11:05.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, let's work hard \Nso we can play live again soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.24,0:11:08.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Then we'll make our major \Ndebut in high school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.74,0:11:10.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We start work next week!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.36,0:11:12.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Come straight here after school!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.56,0:11:14.44,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi. Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.44,0:11:15.80,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.27,0:11:21.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And that first day of work is tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.85,0:11:25.09,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've been in here for thirty minutes now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.09,0:11:27.47,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm bound to catch a cold, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.47,0:11:29.32,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry... I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.32,0:11:31.67,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll work hard at everything except the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.73,0:11:36.09,Default,Futari,0000,0000,0000,,Mom! Sis is drowning!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.20,0:11:43.36,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Catch a cold! Catch a cold! \NCatch a cold! Catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:47.26,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Catch a cold!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.42,0:11:56.61,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Curse this good health of mine...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.28,0:12:00.02,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll just have to fake—
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.27,0:12:05.49,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.49,0:12:06.51,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.51,0:12:08.21,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,First day of work, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.21,0:12:10.35,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I know you're nervous, \Nbut we'll be there for you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.35,0:12:11.41,DefaultItalics,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's work hard together!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.61,0:12:17.79,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,No fair being so nice while \NI'm trying to blow off work...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:26.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You've made me realize the \Nfoolish error of my ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.80,0:12:31.73,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,For making an honest woman out of me, \Nyou have my boundless gratitude.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.64,0:12:35.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,What is she talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:39.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:43.16,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.25,0:12:44.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.28,0:12:45.23,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.32,0:12:46.50,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Do it, Bocchi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.50,0:12:48.74,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Tickets don't go on sale until five o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.39,0:12:51.91,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,We're still getting ready here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.91,0:12:53.62,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She works here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.62,0:12:54.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,She thinks I'm up to no good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.94,0:12:56.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I've got to clear this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.82,0:13:02.17,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-C-C-C-C-Calm down...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:04.13,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who needs to calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.73,0:13:06.53,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the new part-timer?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.53,0:13:08.15,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,You should've just said so.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.15,0:13:09.60,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-S-S-Sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.82,0:13:12.60,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the manager here. Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.96,0:13:15.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,V-Very nice to meet you...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.20,0:13:17.35,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The manager's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.35,0:13:18.94,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't handle people like her.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:20.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika-chan, come here quick!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.25,0:13:24.80,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you're the guitarist \Nwho played in the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.80,0:13:28.07,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Wasn't it... Mango Kamen?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.07,0:13:29.70,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A new nickname?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.21,0:13:31.88,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Manager!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.88,0:13:34.54,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm Mango Kamen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.54,0:13:36.92,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That is {\i1}not{\i0} her name!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.92,0:13:40.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't go giving her weird nicknames, Sis!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.12,0:13:41.20,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sis?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.20,0:13:42.88,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,You're Nijika-chan's sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.88,0:13:44.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I told you before.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.52,0:13:46.49,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,When you first came to Starry, remember?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.35,0:13:51.08,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The club we're gonna play at \Nis called Starry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.08,0:13:54.10,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,My big sister's the manager there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.10,0:13:57.60,Flashback,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, our family lives \Nin the apartments above it.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.15,0:14:00.61,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,My heart was pounding so loud \Nthat I didn't hear her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.61,0:14:02.57,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-R-R-Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.57,0:14:06.21,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That means you don't have to be so nervous.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.21,0:14:07.69,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Right, Sis?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.69,0:14:09.28,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Call me "Manager" here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.76,0:14:12.18,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,And keep our work and private \Nrelationships separate.
Dialogue: 1,0:14:12.64,0:14:15.48,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't scare her like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.87,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H847AB4&\3c&HB9B9C4&\bord1\fs16\fax0.8\frz26.67\pos(228.5,125)}Good Kid\N\h\h\h\h\h\h\hApple 100
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.29,0:14:15.87,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeorgia\c&H091612&\frz225\fs14\fax0.3\pos(485.5,325)}Okaka
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.14,0:14:19.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's clear the tables first.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.29,0:14:21.81,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,When that's done, we'll wipe them all down...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.34,0:14:24.24,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where's Bocchi-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.09,0:14:30.45,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. I needed a breather \Nin a dark, cramped place.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.45,0:14:31.72,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You need a breather already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.65,0:14:36.49,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Here, Bocchi-chan, come over \Nand learn the drinks.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.44,0:14:39.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Tonic water comes out of here,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.68,0:14:42.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and beer comes out of this dispenser.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.00,0:14:43.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,The cocktails are on the shelf behind...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.56,0:14:45.91,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'll never remember it all!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.91,0:14:46.59,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Too fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:49.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I just... mummummmmm...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.21,0:14:54.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have to infuse the knowledge \Ninto me through song!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.36,0:14:55.99,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Where did that come from?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.99,0:14:59.13,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Cocktails are in the rightmost shelf!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.30,0:14:59.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.01,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Tequila!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.13,0:15:01.01,DefaultTop,PA,0000,0000,0000,,They seem fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.56,0:15:01.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad you're learning the drinks,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.01,0:15:02.50,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Vodka!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.84,0:15:04.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but why don't you set the guitar down?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.50,0:15:03.40,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Kahlua!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.40,0:15:04.50,DefaultTop,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Rum!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:07.30,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.85,0:15:09.22,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Weird... She seemed kind of \Ncrappy at the concert, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.30,0:15:09.22,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're not, are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:10.94,Default,PA,0000,0000,0000,,She's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.22,0:15:12.88,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're seriously scaring me!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.96,0:15:15.63,DefaultItalics,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Nijika's trying so hard to stop her, \NI don't think she realizes it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.88,0:15:15.63,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,P-Please! Come back to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:17.12,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.63,0:15:18.22,DefaultItalics,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,But I recognize that sound from somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.22,0:15:18.22,DefaultTop,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hitori-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.35,0:15:20.81,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Get to work!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.96,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Why me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.52,0:15:26.94,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,For drink service, just pour the \Ndrinks they order and hand them over.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.94,0:15:27.92,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.92,0:15:30.86,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,They can pay 500 yen \Non top of the ticket price
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:32.95,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,to get a drink ticket.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.95,0:15:35.38,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,500 yen per drink?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.38,0:15:38.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,And why a drink ticket system?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.22,0:15:41.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Stop staring like it's totally alien to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.56,0:15:45.08,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Clubs like this are actually \Nconsidered restaurants.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.53,0:15:47.35,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know all the details,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.35,0:15:51.84,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,but apparently it's super hard to get a \Nbusiness license to run just a concert venue.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.84,0:15:53.64,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I... I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.64,0:15:58.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,So we offer drinks \Nand operate like a restaurant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.52,0:16:01.22,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.22,0:16:04.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,W-Working at a restaurant is advanced stuff!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.12,0:16:06.90,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe I cleared that bar so soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.30,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Is this... personal growth?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:10.90,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeorgia\b0\c&H525A56&\3c&HEAF2EE&\bord1.8\4c&H5CC7D5&\shad2\pos(497,256.5)}Loneliness Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.12,0:16:14.82,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, customers already!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,We're about to be busy, Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:19.33,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnGeorgia\b0\c&H525A56&\3c&HEAF2EE&\4c&H5CC7D5&\bord1.8\shad2\pos(497,256.5)\t(28,3907,\c&H353836&\3c&H9B9B9B&\4c&H576A63&)}Loneliness Hill
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.28,0:16:17.94,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.33,0:16:22.04,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wait... Customer service already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.04,0:16:23.65,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,What do I say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.65,0:16:26.29,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,"Thank you for your royal parentage..."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.29,0:16:27.28,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.28,0:16:29.68,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just give me a practice run, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.68,0:16:31.80,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,N-No, wait! Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.80,0:16:32.63,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(149,1)\an8\c&H1F242A&\3c&HE8EEEB&\bord2.5}Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.63,0:16:34.84,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(1,97)\an8\fs12\c&H1F242A&\3c&HE8EEEB&\bord2.5\frz358.7\pos(393,232)}Thanks for coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.80,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She closed up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.57,0:16:37.30,Default,Customer A,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me! One cola, please!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.49,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.49,0:16:39.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, cola!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.92,0:16:40.82,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.28,0:16:43.65,Default,Customer B,0000,0000,0000,,I'll have a ginger ale.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.65,0:16:44.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Coming up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.81,0:16:48.28,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, show some \Nrespect for the customers!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.28,0:16:50.45,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,B-B-But I'm not ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.45,0:16:53.98,DefaultItalics,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,We're losing the club's inherent darkness.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.62,0:16:57.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,One oolong and one highball!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:16:58.16,Default,Customer C,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the bathroom?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.76,0:17:00.79,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Down the hall to your right, \Ndoor on the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.79,0:17:03.72,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I experienced no personal growth whatsoever.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.72,0:17:05.29,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.04,0:17:07.76,Default,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Here they are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.79,0:17:11.74,Default,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, there! We're Alexandism!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.30,0:17:15.36,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Our second album goes on sale today,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.72,0:17:15.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,They're pretty good, y'know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.36,0:17:17.64,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,so we're back to doing concerts,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.50,0:17:18.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's a good time to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.40,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,but we hope you all bought it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.60,0:17:20.76,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Once the performances start, \Nwe'll have time to kill.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.40,0:17:22.31,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.76,0:17:21.40,Default,hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.40,0:17:22.31,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:23.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Good work!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.31,0:17:26.88,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,We tried to make every single \Nsong better than our first album,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.25,0:17:24.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you have to sell tickets?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.60,0:17:26.88,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Manager stepped in for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:29.12,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,All of today's bands are really popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.88,0:17:31.02,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,and if you haven't bought it yet, \Nwe're about to play some of those songs,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.12,0:17:31.02,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,so she told me to watch and learn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:33.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's my sister for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.02,0:17:34.25,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,so if you like them, please buy the album!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.11,0:17:36.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,She's a tsun-tsun-tsun-tsun-tsun-tsun-tsun...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.25,0:17:38.23,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,And there's something I want \Nto tell you guys first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:38.23,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,...dere. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:39.30,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Excessive tsun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.23,0:17:41.44,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,The crowd rocked pretty \Nhard at our last concert!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.88,0:17:41.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,S-S-Sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:43.43,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Not only did I fail to help you,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.44,0:17:45.71,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,So after it was over, a guy came up \Nand offered up his card.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.43,0:17:45.71,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't even make eye \Ncontact with the customers.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:47.07,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Want this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.71,0:17:50.59,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,And we were so nervous. "Is this time \Nfor our major debut?" we thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.73,0:17:49.23,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry it's not for mangos.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.23,0:17:50.59,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.59,0:17:52.62,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,But it would look pretty lame to let it show,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:53.67,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You're doing fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.62,0:17:56.51,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,so after a beat we just said, \N"Hello, welcome."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.91,0:17:56.51,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's your first day. You'll get used to it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.51,0:17:57.93,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,"Welcome?"
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:01.23,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Habits can be scary, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.93,0:18:03.85,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-Why are you so nice to a \Nsub-water-flea like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.23,0:18:03.85,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,The words that came out of my mouth
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.85,0:18:08.14,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,were the words I've said a million \Ntimes at my part time job.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.77,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.88,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,According to the guy who gave us his card,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.43,0:18:10.88,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I really like this club.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:16.44,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,he wanted to listen to the band \Non after us today, Tidaman,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.88,0:18:16.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But here and reception are the only places \Nclub staff interact with the customers,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.83,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,but we don't get along with them, \Nand we really wanna outshine them,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.40,0:18:21.83,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,so I want to do my best to make \Nother people like it, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.83,0:18:24.80,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,so we hope you listen to Alexandism too!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.29,0:18:24.21,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm s-s-sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.21,0:18:26.36,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I w-worked so badly at a place \Nthat means so much to you...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:27.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.36,0:18:29.56,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Now, let me introduce the band!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.75,0:18:29.56,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.75,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Always eating curry before a concert, with his \Nown way of doing things... on bass, Matsuda!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.56,0:18:33.75,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I meant I want {\i1}you{\i0} to like \Nthis club too, Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.75,0:18:37.62,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,And the normal guy who always \Nhas our backs... on drums, Rei!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.74,0:18:37.62,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I want us to have fun working,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:39.45,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,and to have fun playing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.62,0:18:43.36,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,He's got so many effects pedals he barely has \Nroom on stage to stand... on guitar, Koichi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.89,0:18:40.68,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Together.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:49.17,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,And on guitar and vocals, without \Nmuch to recommend him... me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.87,0:18:49.17,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,'Course, I also hope you'll be able to speak \Nto customers with a smile some day, too...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.17,0:18:50.30,DefaultTop,Crowd,0000,0000,0000,,Tsuyoshi!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.30,0:18:51.19,DefaultTop,Tsuyoshi,0000,0000,0000,,Let's do this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.76,0:18:53.11,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,It's starting, Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.14,0:19:04.44,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The whole place is united.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.44,0:19:07.12,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The customers and the performers \Nare all enjoying themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.07,0:19:10.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Meanwhile, at my concert...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.88,0:19:15.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,The customers paid 2,000 yen \Nto see that, didn't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.46,0:19:18.37,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,If I stay the way I am,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.37,0:19:23.64,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna give them the same listless \Nconcert next time too, aren't I?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.81,0:19:29.01,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I want to make the effort to change, \Neven if only gradually,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.01,0:19:31.10,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,and enjoy it with the rest of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.10,0:19:32.40,Default,Customer D,0000,0000,0000,,Excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.40,0:19:33.74,Default,Customer D,0000,0000,0000,,Orange juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.74,0:19:34.93,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,C-Coming up...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.50,0:19:51.71,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Look the customer in the eye. Interact.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.27,0:19:54.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.44,0:19:57.78,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Look her in the eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:58.96,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Interact!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.16,0:20:01.97,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,H-Here you are.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.28,0:20:04.60,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan! Your eyes! Your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.60,0:20:05.70,Default,Customer D,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.80,0:20:10.44,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Wow, that was nerve-wracking!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.44,0:20:11.55,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,But great job!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:11.55,0:20:14.46,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,You kept your head above the counter \Nand talked to her!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.33,0:20:16.50,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I did my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.50,0:20:17.07,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.41,0:20:22.45,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Having you here will make my memories \Nof today's concert even more fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.45,0:20:25.45,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And you've taken a step forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.17,0:20:28.31,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A step...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.20,0:20:33.25,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A step.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.16,0:20:38.84,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,A step?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.84,0:20:42.22,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I took a thousand, though!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:47.35,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\c&H3D583C&\pos(320,198.5)}Tickets go on sale at {\c&H25726A&}5 pm
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.35,0:20:48.99,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Good work today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.99,0:20:50.21,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Take care getting home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.21,0:20:50.93,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Bye-bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.93,0:20:52.63,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thank you for having me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.63,0:20:54.62,Default,Seika,0000,0000,0000,,Not leaving, Ryo?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.62,0:20:56.37,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Staying a little while first.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.37,0:20:57.36,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.36,0:20:58.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.90,0:20:59.89,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,See you later!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.89,0:21:03.44,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yes, s-s-s-see you tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.20,0:21:08.24,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.24,0:21:10.48,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I made it through an entire day somehow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.48,0:21:13.41,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,This work thing isn't as hard \Nas I thought it would be!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.41,0:21:15.46,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,I'll do my best again tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.06,0:21:17.08,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Achoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.52,0:21:18.09,Default,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.61,0:21:21.86,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Bocchi worked hard, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.35,0:21:23.38,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.60,0:21:27.12,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,And she managed to say "see you tomorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.12,0:21:27.77,Default,Ryo,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.66,0:21:31.26,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad we formed this band.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.01,0:21:33.00,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, right!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.00,0:21:34.52,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Let's send a LOINE message to Bocchi-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.52,0:21:36.50,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,I'll say, "Let's keep it up tomorrow!"
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.94,0:21:38.94,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(231,1)\an4\c&H6D6D6D&\b0\fs9\pos(248.5,194.5)\3c&HF6F9F6&\bord1.5}Nijika\N\h\h\h\hYou have a message
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.25,0:21:41.96,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,She's got an awful fever.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.96,0:21:44.34,Default,Michiyo,0000,0000,0000,,Dear, prepare a cold compress, would you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.34,0:21:45.88,Default,Naoki,0000,0000,0000,,Does she need a trip to the hospital?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.88,0:21:48.54,DefaultItalics,Hitori,0000,0000,0000,,{\i0}N-Now{\i1} I get the fever...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.88,0:21:53.25,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Now that we've got Bocchi-chan on board...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.25,0:21:54.87,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,All that's left...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:57.43,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,is to find a new vocalist!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.29,0:22:00.56,Default,Girl Student A,0000,0000,0000,,Who's this one for?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.56,0:22:03.54,Default,Kita,0000,0000,0000,,Me, me! It's me, it's me!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.44,0:22:19.89,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The tune that plays when my loneliness \Nand the pedal are stepped on
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.89,0:22:25.44,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Tracks down my cheeks over and over again
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.44,0:22:29.10,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The pounding of my loneliness
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.10,0:22:33.20,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Is joined by the rhythm of the snare drum
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.20,0:22:36.29,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,To create a solid pulse
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.29,0:22:38.82,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Someone, please remove \Nthe distortion on my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.82,0:22:41.79,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,And take a look inside me
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.79,0:22:45.80,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody can get inside my heart
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.80,0:22:49.30,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,But it's the kind of night \Nwhen I hope someone will
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.79,0:22:51.80,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Distortion it's Motion
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.80,0:22:55.23,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Once it starts, there's no stopping it
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.23,0:22:59.45,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Limits can be overwritten with experience
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.45,0:23:00.79,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.79,0:23:02.85,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Distortion is always like that
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.85,0:23:07.31,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,My heart takes off, outpacing my left brain
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.31,0:23:08.95,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Toward where you are
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.95,0:23:11.58,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,An escort to the next note
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:14.30,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Distortion on my day-to-day anguish
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.30,0:23:17.14,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,The chord I play when I'm alone at night
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.14,0:23:18.60,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Is it the same for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.60,0:23:21.22,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,I spent all those days chasing my ideal image
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.22,0:23:25.36,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,Play an F chord with distortion
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.36,0:23:29.40,Songs_ED,ED,0000,0000,0000,,So loud that the needle swings off the scale
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.01,0:23:40.02,Signs,sign,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(3572,1)\fnComic Sans MS\c&H41403D&\3c&HFFFFFF&\b1\bord2\shad2\4c&H4600CF&\pos(309,49.5)}#3  Be Right There
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.55,0:23:39.78,Default,Nijika,0000,0000,0000,,Watch it!